page.title: 01Summary of the entire Block.
page.content: This region is generally agriculturally based. All the squares have a predominant agricultural land cover, ranging from{Enclosed rough {grazing}to{Diciduous woodland.} The{River Dee}flows through this square, from south to north, which accounts for the{Meadowland}which adjoins the river throughout the block. The land in this region is all privately owned by the{Westminster {Estate.}There is also very little unemployment with over half of the inhabitants working directly for the Estate.
